description:
westfield cako is where i usually get my cupcake to crush that sugar crave i have throughout the day. but when one of the girls behind the counter told me they opened one up in metreon with ice cream, i decided to check it out with nothing to do on my hour break anyways. 

First impression: empty. It was sorta quiet over there which i guess was way easier since i didnt have to wait in a line to purchase or sample their ice cream(red velvet and vanilla madagascar a must try!!!!!!!!!!!!) Long story short i bought the pb&j with the tirimisu which lead to getting a stamp on my frequent buyers card and a free cupcake! it was one of the easiest trips to getting my cupcake for the day. 

cant wait until the target over there opens either!!!!!!!!!!! gives me another reason just to swing by metreon(;
